<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还醒着，魔法师！”戴蒙说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪跳到了汤姆的肩膀上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在汤姆耳边小声地说着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴蒙坏笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得把你变成老鼠。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你就可以和猫咪好好玩儿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆挥动了魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下雨！”他紧张地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！玻璃球从天花板上落下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀呀！”玻璃球把戴蒙打得大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴蒙跳开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他撞到了水桶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪从他的两脚间跑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗啦！戴蒙掉进了水桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！”他大叫，“我讨厌水！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴蒙挥动着魔杖，但没有用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆看着猫咪。“你说得对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水能解除戴蒙的魔法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都醒了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干得好，汤姆！”安说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挥动魔杖，把戴蒙捆了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卫兵们把戴蒙送进恐怖地牢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们救出了国王和德克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你救了我们，女儿！”德克大声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是汤姆救了你们，父亲。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克不太高兴地说：“谢谢你，汤姆。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王非常高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要怎么感谢你呢，汤姆？”国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆鞠了个躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的工作，陛下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我用魔法帮助人们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪也很高兴，发出咕噜咕噜的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>